{"tid":1278221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街監狗會同淋病夾埋","createTime":"2019-07-02T11:36:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T11:56:59.000Z","uid":31330,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8b158f8ba5af81e07b7601f88538d2a43ac25bef","tid":1278221,"uid":31330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:36:08.000Z","msg":"今日監狗會開記招話主動調查<br />\n<br />\n擺明就同佢夾埋<br />\n<br />\n入面成班佢地自己人<br />\n<br />\n又無實權，無得傳召班狗調查<br />\n<br />\n查條撚咩<br />\n<br />\n監狗會講左主動調查之後<br />\n<br />\n佢又可以話已經有調查進行緊<br />\n<br />\n唔使成立獨立調查啦<br />\n<br />\n因為無必同時進行兩個調查<br />\n<br />\n或者大家可以等監狗會個調查報告出左先<br />\n<br />\n但係監狗會記招到話要查半年<br />\n<br />\n擺明博香港人善忘<br />\n<br />\n拖佢一年半載之後就冇人再理<br />\n<br />\n到時就更加無人提要獨立調查<br />\n<br />\n真係無恥到極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad8b193f1e7d37acb049e705618905ffd8d691d","tid":1278221,"uid":31330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:36:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"165c1838c73cf4f1697c29b6451f9919dd206910","tid":1278221,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:36:35.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"752b8f65685f7410c852d0a87eb7ec9fa5de0d09","tid":1278221,"uid":31330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:37:16.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁撚賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340a909793a675af2549fcfba5a6642aeec2b66a","tid":1278221,"uid":31330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:39:35.000Z","msg":"淋病真係好撚陰毒"},{"pid":"9a0a613ef3dbbfafe9903186640487779c868b86","tid":1278221,"uid":31330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:41:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01a6da07765b9c2542b667386f8deb473ffc15e7","tid":1278221,"uid":31330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:41:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hat